INDYMAC FEDERAL BANK, FSB, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Marisa L. BELL, Defendant-Petitioner. 079500
C-78 September Term 2017 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 22, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION.

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002510-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
